{
  "stem": "1775.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a little opening, just as big as this seat of the chair, where we went out, just at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All day, we were sitting, our [INAUDIBLE] our legs crisscrossed, or laying on the back, or laying on the side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when anybody laid on their back, the rest had to lay on their back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if somebody turned on their side, everybody had to turn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they-- very cramped, very cramped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everything was done all day in the-- in the bunker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were there-- first, we were there six weeks, but that was another bunker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the bunker that the men had built, before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then, when we left and we came, and there was more of us, we had to build a larger bunker.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we built a larger bunker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we built a bunker for seven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they eighth-- the eighth girl came, so it became really cramped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were there from when we came back, after Sukkot, like October, we were there until the last three weeks before we were liberated, when we ran away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were there like October, November, December, January, February, March, April, May, and June.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five kilometers away from Meserich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I spent all my life in the war years, and after the war years-- everything was around by [INAUDIBLE] Meserich.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything I did was around Meserich-- five kilometers this way, eight kilometers the other way, but always around-- because I wasn't familiar with anything else.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew if I go anyplace else, I'm going to get killed, because I didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't know any people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But here, at least I knew-- I knew somebody, and that somebody knew me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's-- that's where I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
